    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A GPAI model that presents systemic risks. GPAI models present systemic risks when they have high impact capabilities based on technical tools and methodologies, when the cumulative amount of compute used for training is greater than 10^25 FLOPs, or when the Commission determines high impact capabilities."
